[112.449021, "o", "📊 Generated 3 signed transactions:\r\n\r\n─── Tx 1 of 3 ───\r\n   Address: bcrt1qemc66j6ak73sr36muuanwn9thgkr0ygcuu45gr\r\n   Dust:    800 sats → miner fees\r\n   Hex:     \r\n\r\n─── Tx 2 of 3 ───\r\n   Address: bcrt1qw2v5zv6tyykc9nf3zhrn5aa7lss3zlr4ej0l9y\r\n   Dust:    500 sats → miner fees\r\n   Hex:     \r\n\r\n─── Tx 3 of 3 ───\r\n   Address: bcrt1qqrh0eykt4y8upwyzspkjf8m8jmmsfdh825rmsz\r\n   Dust:    300 sats → miner fees\r\n   Hex:     \r\n\r\n💡 Broadcast each transaction:\r\n   bitcoin-cli -rpcport=18443 -rpcuser=user -rpcpassword=pass sendrawtransaction <hex>\r\n\r\n⚠️  Broadcast at different times to prevent timing correlation.\r\n   Miners may batch these transactions together automatically.\r\n"]
